{
  "stem": "26140.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when a few of them, about 10 of them, came out of there, they took them to the penalty company, which most likely, I doubt they survived.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the main camp, Auschwitz camp number one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were a big accommodation, big room, which people lied on the floor first, because we had no beds.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, they-- so they made some beds, three-- three tier beds, where we-- we slept on a straw mattress.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we all-- well, I stayed with my twin brother, my older brother stayed in different block, where he-- where he was living separate.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, in the morning, you had a gong giving you time 6 o'clock to get up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the kapos came into the room with sticks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whoever was slowing getting up, they moved-- beat them up to get ready.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had a quick wash in cold water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then an appel, where-- a roll up, they call it in English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a roll up where we were counted and then moved to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the beginning, the work was very hard, unloading bricks or digging trenches, which, at the beginning, was not so bad, but later on, I felt, with the amount of food I am consuming, that I have no strength left to carry on with the-- with the speed.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had once, coffee in the morning, watery coffee, then soup, beetroot soup, or whatever watery soup they gave us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, in the evening, we had a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's-- that's about all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had to consume as much as I can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later on, I tried to see if I could get anywhere something to-- to compensate for the lack of food.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
